Enlight's Odem Partnership Gets Credit Line to Build 40 Solar Stations

-- B y   S u s a n   L e r n e r
-- 
2011-02-22T09:06:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/enlight-s-odem-partnership-gets-credit-line-to-build-40-solar-stations.html
  Enlight Renewable Energy Ltd . said
Odem-Enlight LP signed a credit line of as much as 22.2 million
shekels with Bank Hapoalim Ltd. The financing will be used to
build up to 40 photovoltaic power stations, according to a
statement filed today with the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susan Lerner in Jerusalem at 
 slerner2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
